result.text: Three days is not enough to comprehend a place as big as Anhui, let alone China. But if you're willing to learn one thing about China every day, you'll become an expert on China in a few years. I have worked in Anhui for over five years, and am glad to have the chance to introduce Anhui to these young professionals and students. It's a pity many foreigners don't have a chance to come to China to see the country for themselves, but believe what they see from media. Seeing is believing. China is way better than you thought.
